text: Icaro (Quechua: ikaro) is a South American indigenous colloquialism for magic song. Icaro may also refer to: * CV Ícaro, previous name of Club 15-15, a Spanish women's professional volleyball team * Icaro (manga), a 1997 Japanese manga series * Icaro 2000, an Italian aircraft manufacturer, including a list of aircraft * Icaro Air, a former airline based in Quito, Ecuador * "Icaro", a song by Chana from the 2008 EP Manos Arriba ==See also== * Icara (disambiguation) * Icaros (disambiguation)
title: Icaro (disambiguation)
